        <strong>Instructor Overview: The CANDOR Process (~15 min)</strong>
        <p>Start here. Watch the recorded lecture where Dr. Bradham walks you through the CANDOR framework, its five components, and why Communication and Resolution Programs represent a paradigm shift in how organizations respond to patient harm events.</p>
